text: "Feeling Myself" is a hip-hop song by Trinidadian-American rapper Nicki Minaj. It also features American singer-songwriter Beyoncé. It was released on December 15, 2014. It was also recorded in the same year the song was released (2014). It is from Minaj's third studio album, The Pinkprint. It was written by Minaj, SZA, Beyoncé, and Hit-Boy. It spent 20 weeks on the Billboard Hot 100 making it a world record for the longest charting non-single by a female rapper. The song's lyrics are intense, and brag about the two musicians. ==References== Category:Nicki Minaj songs Category:Beyoncé songs Category:Hip hop songs Category:2014 songs
